spec_data.Name: rubygem-activerecord-nulldb-adapter
spec_data.Description:
A database backend that translates database interactions into no-ops. Using
NullDB enables you to test your model business logic - including after_save
hooks - without ever touching a real database.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 21 Feb 2017 06:33:53 PM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: The Null Object pattern as applied to ActiveRecord database adapters
